g.text: Asks to write a Report/Diagnosis about a Test
This method is repeated in other methods on the code,
but on this Diagram it will appear only in here,
as it defines the wanted variable.
[reportDateBoolean is false and resultDateBoolean is true]
This method is a method from the Collections used by Java,
it is represented in this Sequence Diagram because without its representation,
the Sequence would not be as comprehensible.
[Until the Specialist Doctor decides to leave or until there are no more Test to do a Report on]
Shows the list of Tests without Report/Diagnosis
Chooses one Test (with Result and without Report)
Asks for confirmation of the selected Test
Confirms the Test to the report on
[For each Test Parameter of the chosen Test]
Shows the results of the Test and asks for data (text)
Asks for confirmation of the given data
Asks if the Specialist Doctor wants to write another
Decides if he wants to write another Report
